{"tid":914873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真支爆！支那工廠爆炸　現恐怖焦黑大坑","createTime":"2018-11-24T15:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T18:41:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c245089ffb8ce65a3185c92790a4a48a57614d02","tid":914873,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181124/s00004/bc7dd2f3bd17ada4fbf862b29cbd477c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181124%2Fs00004%2Fbc7dd2f3bd17ada4fbf862b29cbd477c.jpg&h=d0ee389e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181124/s00004/bc816b12d53d0f72179d20d62546bc52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181124%2Fs00004%2Fbc816b12d53d0f72179d20d62546bc52.jpg&h=c292cc65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181124/s00004/bc836011e34ab23f8b00d0fa8f2d7f79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181124%2Fs00004%2Fbc836011e34ab23f8b00d0fa8f2d7f79.jpg&h=bc9efe91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吉林省東豐縣三合鄉永安村三組的吉林省江城機械公司，23日（周五）晚上約11時40分，發生爆炸並引起火災，事故已造成2人死57人受傷，其中1人危殆。涉事企業負責人已被捕。<br />\n<br />\n吉林省江城機械公司廢舊倉庫堆料場據指是因易燃易爆物引起爆炸，造成周圍部分房屋不同程度受損，爆炸波及數公里範圍。《新京報》引述一名目擊者稱，他睡覺時忽然聽到爆炸聲，「跟放鞭炮似的」。<br />\n<br />\n另一名居民稱，她晚上11時關燈睡覺，此後忽然聽到響聲，一開始還以為發生了地震。「我是第一時間起來的，起來就找我家人，把孩子抓（抱）起來。」這名居民稱，「我這臉、腿、腳，都讓玻璃扎了。我出來一看，滿天都是火星。」爆炸引發周邊部分房屋倒塌，一名死者家屬稱，「姊姊爬出來了，姊夫卻沒了」。 <br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，24日（周六）上午，明火已撲滅，但仍有大量濃煙，氣味刺鼻。事發地附近方圓2公里的部分房屋、建築外牆和玻璃不同程度受損，一些房子屋頂被震掉。東豐縣官方微博發布的消息稱，截至24日12時40分，共查出受損房屋370戶，其中輕微受損282戶，鑑定需大修73戶，徹底倒塌15戶。當地官方正組織災後受損房屋的修繕工作，對於輕微受損的282戶房屋，由三合鄉政府和所在村黨支部組織村民自行維修；對徹底倒塌的房屋，將由江城機械公司負責無償再建。<br />\n<br />\n吉林省東豐縣互聯網信息中心通報，截止24日下午5時，已設置群眾安置點，發放禦寒衣物，緊急調運礦泉水100箱，即食麵100箱，救災棉被100牀，和塑料薄膜1376公斤等，保障群眾基本生活。當局同時接收省應急管理廳救災棉衣300件和棉被褥300套。東豐縣政府網站發佈文章稱，涉事企業負責人被控制。另經調查，此次事件排除屬暴恐行為。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）"},{"pid":"00addc509bfffeabe45420fbc1acfb5104bcc092","tid":914873,"uid":220701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"事故已造成2人死57人受傷，其中1人危殆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4ef2b28179d987cc7488e9be98e2a882d53fdc","tid":914873,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:14:55.000Z","msg":"點可能會死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe7f6a7b50648d258688449a265303b12493c3a","tid":914873,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"支那媒體又講大話 區區爆炸點會有支那人死"},{"pid":"d4e24a8aaf924a9f76cee2960e4ad0f2447c6ffe","tid":914873,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc88cbebaf148c95df428d0e88d8244ec9815601","tid":914873,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/232533_b47770faf22e25c2acf599a1ef87fd42.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F232533_b47770faf22e25c2acf599a1ef87fd42.gif&h=58759685&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"946b6b695357fcec8663553fac33a4792017d789","tid":914873,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc88cbebaf148c95df428d0e88d8244ec9815601","tid":914873,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/232533_b47770faf22e25c2acf599a1ef87fd42.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2